Login:
admin/hackme can deal with the Admin and Profile endpoints but by default has no access to data

To give the admin user access to data you need to call the profiles/register endpoint which we recommend you do for the batch user.

batch/123 is a default user for batch operations that is not an administrator but should have access to your company data
